text: The 2005 K2 League season operates its season in two stages, with the winners of each stage to the post-season championship playoffs. In the event of the same team winning both stages, there will be no playoff. ==League standing== === First stage === === Second Stage === ==Championship Playoff== ===Final=== 1st leg 2nd leg Incheon Korail won 4–2 on aggregate. ==Winner== ==See also== * 2005 K-League Category:Korea National League seasons K
